CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 21, 1941, pg. 14 reads: "Lots of fun was enjoyed by the pupils of the Robert L. Vann(formerly Watt) school at the school's annual picnic last week...Below: Views of West View Park and the children enjoying the amusements. ' Harris photo."
TitMainTitle: Amusement ride at West View Park, during annual picnic for Robert L. Vann Elementary School
